                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                                        <placeName>Kingston Jamaica</placeName>\n                                        <date>Rosh hodesh</date>\n                              </p>\n                              <p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                                        <date>Sivan 5611.</date>\n                              </p>\n                              <p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                                        <date>Sunday June 11th</date>\n                              </p>\n                              <p>\n                                        <addressee>Revd I Leeser</addressee>\n                              </p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(2)\">Respected Friend</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(4)\">Your favor of <date>May 6th</date><lb/> came duly\n                                        to hand giving much regret at<lb/> the ingratitude practiced\n                                        towards you. But<lb/> you have that written which must\n                                        baffle all<lb/> all the efforts of your enemies; the\n                                        cannot<lb/> eqult<add>?</add> long and in their exultation\n                                        of (what<lb/> they may <hi rend=\"underline\">term</hi> your\n                                        defeat) they must be<lb/> condemned by the <add>?</add> and\n                                        more enlight-<lb/>ened portion of the world to which\n                                        your<lb/> devotion to their service has been known<lb/> I\n                                        trust that your literary efforts will meet<lb/> with more\n                                                  <hi rend=\"underline\">praising</hi><add>?</add>\n                                        encouragement<lb/> than they do here: the few readers there\n                       